  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK974">
<l>orumai makaḷirē pōlap perumaiyun </l>
<l>taṉṉaittāṉ koṇṭoḻuki ṉuṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even greatness, like a woman's chastity, belongs only to him who guards himself.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
